<div class='otherEdition' id='edition_198167'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/198167.Roots"><img alt="Roots: The Saga of an American Family" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442820985i/198167._UY200_.jpg" />
