        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer23752307" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6721065070209731979">I appreciate the author&apos;s research of his own roots and the overall message this book has. The problem I had with it was that the writing style was uninteresting. It wasn&apos;t bad but it made the characters too two-dimensional for me to enjoy the story overall. They were all empty and I couldn&apos;t cheer for them or feel for them. But I understand why the book is important to some and why it has the position it has, I just didn&apos;t notice the literary value it supposedly has. Plus the plagiarism accusat</span>
  <span id="freeText6721065070209731979" style="display:none">I appreciate the author's research of his own roots and the overall message this book has. The problem I had with it was that the writing style was uninteresting. It wasn't bad but it made the characters too two-dimensional for me to enjoy the story overall. They were all empty and I couldn't cheer for them or feel for them. But I understand why the book is important to some and why it has the position it has, I just didn't notice the literary value it supposedly has. Plus the plagiarism accusations can't be good for an author's reputation and respect.</span>
