<div id="review_832646612" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/832646612" />
    <a title="P.S. Winn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/23133809-p-s-winn"><img alt="P.S. Winn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1518929518p2/23133809.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/832646612?book_show_action=true">Jan 23, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="P.S. Winn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="P.S. Winn" href="/user/show/23133809-p-s-winn">P.S. Winn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer832646612" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2835864582390588158">If you haven&apos;t read this amazing story, you have to grab it. The author not only found his own past but has shared it with readers in a remarkable way. You can&apos;t help but fall in love with the family and empathize with their plight. Some day I woiuld love to be able to look up my own ancestors and find the lives they came before and the legacy left behind, great job!</span>
  <span id="freeText2835864582390588158" style="display:none">If you haven't read this amazing story, you have to grab it. The author not only found his own past but has shared it with readers in a remarkable way. You can't help but fall in love with the family and empathize with their plight. Some day I woiuld love to be able to look up my own ancestors and find the lives they came before and the legacy left behind, great job!</span>
