<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17708215391012508200">Alexander Murray Palmer Haley was an American writer. He is best known as the author of <i>Roots: The Saga of an American Family</i>, and of <i>The Autobiography of Malcolm X</i>, the latter of which he wrote in collaboration with Malcolm X.</span>

</div>
